Package org.firebirdsql.jna.fbclient

Interface WinFbClientLibrary

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.sun.jna.AltCallingConvention, FbClientLibrary, com.sun.jna.Library, com.sun.jna.win32.StdCall, com.sun.jna.win32.StdCallLibrary
    public interface WinFbClientLibrary
extends FbClientLibrary, com.sun.jna.win32.StdCallLibrary
    JNA library interface specifically for the Windows platform.

    This interface instructs JNA to apply __stdcall conventions.

    Warning: Some methods defined in ibase.h (those marked with ISC_EXPORT_VARARG) apply __cdecl, so those methods might break.

    Since:
    3.0
